                            <comment id="16842103" author="karlpauls" created="Fri, 17 May 2019 11:21:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ashokpanghal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ashokpanghal&quot;&gt;ashokpanghal&lt;/a&gt;,&#160;thanks. It seems like this is a continuation of the work done in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4746&quot; title=&quot;Escape outputting filter parameter in service servlet&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-4746&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-4746&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Can you merge the two together (it seems like you ignore the escapeHtml method added there - I think there is no reason not to just extend it maybe)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
